[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    175[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Location:** Additional Resources section, "AWS Sample Repos" and "Operations Research in Healthcare"
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    176[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    177[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **The problem:** Two TODO items appear in the published recipe:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    178[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Find and verify relevant aws-samples repos for optimization/scheduling patterns (RECIPE-GUIDE requires 3-5 sample repos per recipe) -->`
