[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    181[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The RECIPE-GUIDE requires 3-5 sample repos per recipe. The recipe currently has zero verified sample repos. This is a structural gap against the recipe guide requirements, not just a cosmetic placeholder.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    182[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    183[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** The writer needs to search for and verify relevant aws-samples repos (e.g., `amazon-sagemaker-examples` for forecasting patterns, any OR-Tools or optimization examples in AWS contexts, Batch job submission patterns). The INFORMS Healthcare conference proceedings or the journal "Operations Research for Health Care" are legitimate references that should be verified and linked. This is a blocking item per the RECIPE-GUIDE.
